---
import WidgetLayout from '../../layouts/WidgetLayout.astro';
---
<WidgetLayout title="Dialog">
  <h1>Dialog</h1>
  <p>Modal overlay with focus trap.</p>

  <h2>Preview</h2>
  <pre class="ascii-mockup">┌─────────────────────────────┐
│                             │
│  ┌ Confirm ──────────────┐  │
│  │                       │  │
│  │  Shuffle the deck?    │  │
│  │                       │  │
│  │  ▸ Yes     No         │  │
│  └───────────────────────┘  │
│                             │
└─────────────────────────────┘</pre>

  <h2>Props</h2>
  <table>
    <thead><tr><th>Prop</th><th>Type</th><th>Notes</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td>title</td><td>string?</td><td></td></tr>
      <tr><td>children</td><td>ReactNode</td><td></td></tr>
      <tr><td>onClose</td><td>function?</td><td></td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h2>Usage</h2>
  <pre><code>&lt;Dialog title="Confirm" onClose={'{'}handleClose{'}'}&gt;
  &lt;Text&gt;Shuffle the deck?&lt;/Text&gt;
  &lt;Button label="Yes" onPress={'{'}handleYes{'}'} /&gt;
  &lt;Button label="No" onPress={'{'}handleNo{'}'} /&gt;
&lt;/Dialog&gt;</code></pre>

  <h2>Custom overlays with primitives</h2>
  <p>Build custom overlays with the primitives directly:</p>
  <pre><code>// Tooltip (high-z, no focus trap)
&lt;Box z={'{'}100{'}'} position="absolute" left={'{'}x{'}'} top={'{'}y{'}'}&gt;...&lt;/Box&gt;

// Inline focus trap (no overlay)
&lt;FocusTrap&gt;&lt;WizardStep /&gt;&lt;/FocusTrap&gt;</code></pre>

  <h2>Interactive demo</h2>
  <div class="demo-placeholder">Interactive demo coming soon</div>
</WidgetLayout>
